summary: Say hello to Kirstte. A female Nord Racemenu Preset.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4][b]Description:
[/b][/size]Hello everyone. Say hello to a Racemenu Preset I've made. (These are surprisingly fun to make as mods when I'm board.)

Here's Kirstte Wolf-Child. She's a Nord.

Requirements to make her match pics:
[list]
[*]RaceMenu
[*]Hair: KS's Hairdos
[*] Skin: Fair Skin Complexion
[*] Eye Meshes: Skyrim's Ultimate Eyemeshes Ruhmastered 
[*]Eye Textures: GCO - Van Gogh Eyes 
[*]Face: Pretty Face 
[*]Northborn Scars 
[*]XCE Warpaint and Dirt
[/list][size=4][color=#0000ff][b]Install:
[/b][/color][/size]Drop contents into data folder.

[size=4][color=#ff0000][b]Uninstall:
[/b][/color][/size]Delete the related files of the mod.
